18
00:02:58,613 --> 00:02:59,132
Qing.

19
00:03:02,010 --> 00:03:03,510
What saint are you pretending to be?

20
00:03:03,733 --> 00:03:04,333
Just now,

21
00:03:04,733 --> 00:03:06,613
I clearly saw you flirting
with my Qing.

22
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,290
Acting aroused in front
of your daughter-in-law,

23
00:03:09,773 --> 00:03:10,853
do you have no shame?

24
00:03:12,013 --> 00:03:12,652
Qing.

25
00:03:13,333 --> 00:03:15,652
Why are you having hysterics
first thing in the morning?

26
00:03:17,132 --> 00:03:18,092
Look clearly.

27
00:03:18,293 --> 00:03:19,372
I am your Father!

28
00:03:19,493 --> 00:03:21,013
